Muchidzidzo che[[Kupimanzvimbo]], [[mutsazanisi]] (equator), mutsetse unoratidza panosangana uso hweurungano nemutsendo unocheka [[akiso yekuzeya]] ''(axis of rotation)'' kwe[[urungano]] yacho negonya re 90<sup>o</sup>. Kureva kuti [[mutsendo]] uyu wakaita mutwi neakiso. Chimwe chinoonekwa kuti [[goko rehuremu]] ''(centre of mass)'' yeurungano iri pamutsendo iwoyu zvakare.  Vara guru rinoshandiswa kana pari kutsangudzwa Mutsazanisi rweRinopasi, (Earth).

Takatarisana neRinopasi, [[Mutsazanisi]] mutsetse wekufungidzira une nhambwe dzakaenzana kubva ku[[North Pole]] kusvika ke[[South Pole]] panzvimbo dzose. Mutsetse uyu unocheka urungano yeRinopasi kuita zvikamu zviviri zvakaenzana.

[[North pole]] ndipo pa[[chimiso]] panosangana uso neakiso yekuzeya yeRinopasi (Earth), kuri ku[[maodzanyemba]] kweRinopasi, riri divi rakapesana ne''South pole'' . 

[[South pole]] ndipo pachimiso panosangana uso neakiso yekuzeya yeRinopasi (Earth), kuri ku[[chamhembe]] kweRinopasi. 

==Kuronda nzvimbo panyika==

Muchidzidzo che[[Jekanyika]] (Geodesy), nyika yakatarwa nemhando mbiri dzemitsetse. Kune mitsetse yakatarwa yakati sambamba ne[[Mutsazanisi]] inonzi [[lattitude]]; kune mitsetse yakatarwa ichibata kuNorth pole neSouth pole inonzi [[longitude]]. Mitsetse iyi inoshevedzwa nenhamba dzakarongeka. Nhamba dzemitsetse yelattitude dzinoveregwa dzichibva paMutsazanisi dzichienda kumavirira nekumadokero. Nhamba dzemitsetse yelongitude dzinoverengwa dzichibva pamutsetse we[[Greenwich Meridian]]  zvichienda kuNorth pole neSouth pole. Greenwich Meridian mutsetse welongitude unopfuura pedyo ne[[Royal Observatory, Greenwich]],ku[[United Kingdom]]. Naizvozvo nzvimbo dzose dziri panyika dzine nhamba inotaura kuti nzvimbo iri papi mudandemutande remitsetse iyi.  Ruzivo urwu ndirwo rwakashandiswa muhumhizha hwe[[GPS]], [[Geographical Position System]] chinova chombo chinobatsira kutaura kuti tiri papi uye kupa [[rudzivo]] rwenzvimbo yatinoda kuenda.  


